Class Value

  • java.lang.Object
    • Value
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanValue, IntegerValue, RealValue, StringValue

    public abstract class Value
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class for a specific primitive value. There are four possible values: Integer, Real, Boolean and String.
